h3. Step to Replicate
# Create a event with the following option
#* Uncheck {{All Day event}}
#* Set {{Repeat}} to weekly
#* Set {{when}}:
#** From: {{02-Oct-2015}}  {{08:00}}
#** To : {{02-Oct-2015}} {{9:00}}
# Edit  one of the event and modify the following 
#* Check the {{this instance only}}
#* Set the time to the following:
#**  From {{9:00}}
#** To {{10:00}}
# Save (at this point you will see the edited event time will change which is expected)
# Edit the same event again but uncheck the {{Edit this instance only}}
# Save

Observed Behaviour:
The edited event is appear at the start of the repeat event date. The other event are not affected by the changes that you made even though the {{Edit this instance only}} option is unchecked. 

Please refer to the video attached to this ticket for the detailed steps to replicate the issue.

